{{Expand Spanish|Eduardo García Máynez|date=November 2011}} '''Eduardo García Máynez''' (January 11, 1908 &ndash; September 2, 1993) was a academic, jurist and philosopher of Mexican law. Member of the National college, managing Director of Instituto Tecnologico Autonomo de Mexico, teacher of UNAM, general secretary and researcher of Instituto de Investigaciones Filosoficas and weiter of some works important of the law .
